{"tid":2091804,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一個熱門POST，就睇到幾多連登仔中標題黨同唔ＦＣ","createTime":"2020-07-03T01:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T12:56:00.000Z","uid":94771,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"4230fb4ef943550cad97b35b62784012617eccda","tid":2091804,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"用中文角度你用<br />\n［立場：］即係想表達出係立場官方講，<br />\n但實際睇返個Source，你就可以知道依編文根本唔係立場官方寫，而係立場投稿<br />\n<br />\n原文係：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">徐然<br />\n80 後廢中，憤世嫉俗；寧鳴而生，不默而死；留一口氣，點一盞燈。<br />\n在批鬥《立場》之前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020/7/2 &mdash; 22:14</span></ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%A8%E6%89%B9%E9%AC%A5-%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4-%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%25AC%25A5-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2589%258D%2F%23&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=2d7cc4e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%25AC%25A5-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2589%258D%2F%23&h=4616989c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%A8%E6%89%B9%E9%AC%A5-%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4-%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D/#</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後原文樓主又唔比返Source你地，<strong><ins>佢背後用意就大家自己諗啦</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n同樓主講，樓主就話立場出得依個投稿即係等於立場絕對同意作者立場，所以視為立場官方立場。<br />\n如果咁都講得通，咁立場之前有民主黨投稿，又有本土投稿，又有獨派出文投稿<br />\n所場立場的<strong><ins>立場官方</ins></strong>係唔係就係<strong>泛民，本土，獨立光譜的合體</strong>？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>重新一次，立場影手足大頭係抵屌的，屌係正常。<br />\n但唔好用下三流老屈的方式去屌，咁做只顯得自己人格好卑賤。</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>誤導標題的熱門</ins></strong><br />\n立場：要求幫當事人打格同黑警有咩分別<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2091590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2091590</a>"},{"pid":"72bb6657322e70a63f5bfc1c388a2b685377b7d0","tid":2091804,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果依編野上佐熱門，我應該會原ＰＯＳＴ樓主咬"},{"pid":"79e5b455f3b6108428a19c8f6b6cdca8b99cb688","tid":2091804,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72bb6657322e70a63f5bfc1c388a2b685377b7d0","tid":2091804,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果依編野上佐熱門，我應該會原ＰＯＳＴ樓主咬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68de501accc9123d370c9c87967246f61227f3f5","tid":2091804,"uid":94771,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:13:49.000Z","msg":"原Post樓主 <br />\n<br />\n唔講係投稿<br />\n唔比Source<br />\n故意誤導<br />\n<br />\n自己諗下發生咩事啦"},{"pid":"87b4a0fa3dc1a5cf95059ed22467d4f276b969bb","tid":2091804,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de8d88a08a05ed9ab25921e701b3df215cdd04f4","tid":2091804,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b371947653fc1faeb965095b7b8aaa87d12ffb77","tid":2091804,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:15:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30483c10696962e49f0078f7c6765ccf9e339866","tid":2091804,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:16:14.000Z","msg":"misleading<img src=\"/assets/